---
import PublicLayout from "../layouts/PublicLayout.astro";
---

<PublicLayout title="CannaLog - Home" description="Welcome to CannaLog">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-32 dark:text-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold leading-tight mb-4">
        Your Personal Cannabis Journey, Demystified.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
        CannaLog is a mindful companion for tracking, understanding, and
        optimizing your cannabis experiences. Gain insights, find what works for
        you, and cultivate well-being.
      </p>
      <a
        href="#"
        class="inline-block bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-700 px-8 py-4 text-white font-bold rounded-lg shadow-lg transform hover:scale-105 transition duration-300 dark:bg-secondary-500 dark:text-white"
      >
        Start Logging for Free
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="">
    <div
      class="gap-16 items-center py-8 px-4 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 lg:py-16 lg:px-6"
    >
      <div class="font-light">
        <h2 class="mb-4 text-4xl tracking-tight font-extrabold">
          Your Journey, Illuminated
        </h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          CannaLog is more than a journal; it's your personal cartographer for
          the cannabis landscape. We help you connect the dots between cultivar,
          dosage, and your state of mind, transforming subjective feelings into
          actionable insights. By mindfully charting your sessions, you move
          beyond guesswork and start making intentional choices that truly
          enhance your well-being.
        </p>
        <p>
          Discover which terpenes uplift your creativity or what timing promotes
          restful sleep. Our intuitive tools empower you to build a personalized
          routine that is both effective and mindful.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-8">
        <img
          class="w-full rounded-lg"
          src="https://flowbite.s3.amazonaws.com/blocks/marketing-ui/content/office-long-2.png"
          alt="office content 1"
        />
        <img
          class="mt-4 w-full lg:mt-10 rounded-lg"
          src="https://flowbite.s3.amazonaws.com/blocks/marketing-ui/content/office-long-1.png"
          alt="office content 2"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="">
